":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"滿州國同北洋政府都係被抹黑得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"北洋尚可為之辯護，為滿洲國辯護就做多咗啦，溥儀身為滿洲國皇帝，連路過自己祖墳都被日本人夾住唔可以過去鞠個躬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對滿族冇乜興趣，純粹覺得滿州國發展得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf39163b56e9bff6808b88282155bb52f07aad1","tid":858334,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"北洋政府點都係好過偽國民政府嘅,但國民黨都改喇.<br />\n依家應該將中華民國去國民黨化先o岩,換番五色旗同國徽!"},{"pid":"4fc518891794c5ad33d57182d30727f020f59626","tid":858334,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://goo.gl/cMVWz3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FcMVWz3&h=61238077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/中國聯合準備銀行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKodibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dcf09824\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/中國聯合準備銀行</a><br />\n<br />\n中國聯合準備銀行成立於1938年3月1日，是中華民國臨時政府在北京設立的發券銀行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/中華民國臨時政府_(1937年－1940年)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C_%281937%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8D1940%E5%B9%B4%29&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKodibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dd310157\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/中華民國臨時政府_(1937年－1940年)</a><br />\n<br />\n中華民國臨時政府，是大日本帝國在中國抗日戰爭期間成立的傀儡政權，於1937年12月14日在北京成立，統轄平津和華北等地區。為與中華民國維新政府相區別，又稱華北臨時政府。以五色旗為國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empire_of_Japan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEmpire_of_Japan&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKodibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7ccc179a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Empire_of_Japan</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/52/Second_world_war_asia_1937-1942_map_en6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F5%2F52%2FSecond_world_war_asia_1937-1942_map_en6.png&h=be4a02c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/鬼畜米英\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fja.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%AC%BC%E7%95%9C%E7%B1%B3%E8%8B%B1&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKodibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2171446b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/鬼畜米英</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kotobank.jp/word/同文同種\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkotobank.jp%2Fword%2F%E5%90%8C%E6%96%87%E5%90%8C%E7%A8%AE&d=pY0agEH7gCaDRQKpRecKodibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9099ab1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://kotobank.jp/word/同文同種</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/QCoZAy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FQCoZAy&h=d753b880&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f1437b50f93aa3dcc5197780ccf4df686de9f8c","tid":858334,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf39163b56e9bff6808b88282155bb52f07aad1","tid":858334,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"北洋政府點都係好過偽國民政府嘅,但國民黨都改喇.<br />\n依家應該將中華民國去國民黨化先o岩,換番五色旗同國徽!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"應該用辛亥革命既鐵血十八星旗<br />\n18粒星代表關內十八漢族行省<br />\n非漢族地區自行公投決定獨立成國定係維持中國領土"}]}